{"tid":2026208,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「光復香港-時代革命」其中一位作者 梁頌恆 直至今時今日依然俾人話係鬼","createTime":"2020-05-20T20:11:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T05:18:47.000Z","uid":344304,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d8fdc311315953db66560c78997040c06d186b1e","tid":2026208,"uid":344304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T20:11:30.000Z","msg":"岩先碌碌下立場fb發現佢有個專訪 下面留言既人同四年前依然無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/standnewshk/posts/3097495420336057\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fposts%2F3097495420336057&d=JWMo9xAWlgSpyjxIujWPsZHrfcRVF4fwerrMnmH2A0w%3D&h=2c20b8d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/standnewshk/posts/3097495420336057</a><br />\n<br />\n9成罵佢地搞屎棍 得1成幫口 同當時既公海一樣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n話佢知道選舉近 出黎r水<br />\n事實佢keep住有出黎遊行兼嗌咪叫人捐星火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大聲責難tvb鳩報新聞-跌左隻耳仔<br />\n但仲拎tvb精心剪輯既的士圖黎串佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事實佢三年前當日留到好夜 速龍都出埋先走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n收左中共錢搞亂香港抗爭<br />\n但從來無拎過實際證據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">反而15年區議會青年新政不受鄭永健利誘界票 仲報埋icac</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><a href=\"https://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2019/07/28/197626#關於「光復香港，時代革命」\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Farticles%2F2019%2F07%2F28%2F197626%23%E9%97%9C%E6%96%BC%E3%80%8C%E5%85%89%E5%BE%A9%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%EF%BC%8C%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3%E9%9D%A9%E5%91%BD%E3%80%8D&d=JWMo9xAWlgSpyjxIujWPsZHrfcRVF4fwerrMnmH2A0w%3D&h=1086f917\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2019/07/28/197626#關於「光復香港，時代革命」</a></span><br />\n喺2016年嘅一月下旬，<span style=\"color: red;\">天琦約左青年新政嘅召集人梁頌恆同另一位成員上當時本民前位於土瓜灣嘅辦公室商討選舉策略</span>。（因當時本民前缺乏選舉經驗，所以好多時都會向有區選經驗以及時有合作嘅青年新政請教）因為覺得當時嘅口號唔夠搶耳，立場亦唔夠鮮明，所以當晚幾個人就喺Office嘅露台構思新嘅選舉口號。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一堆無根無據既指控 純粹出自熱狗對青年新政/老泛民大中華膠對本土派既仇恨<br />\n到今時今日仍然流竄於野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諷刺既係佢地竟然可以當無件事咁去騎劫本土派既口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"865ef74de9d9c2ed9cce483509913f9b381c9cff","tid":2026208,"uid":835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T20:16:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34eabeba63adfa1bd6718a23c4daca12402c4d96","tid":2026208,"uid":344304,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T20:25:47.000Z","msg":"諗返起<br />\n<br />\n早半年 林鄭公開批判光復香港 時代革命係搞港獨 搞革命同中央政府作對<br />\n<br />\n成班老泛民kol同埋好多連登仔 嚇到瀨晒屎標晒尿 叫人唔好再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會得罪中立撚 嚇走淺黃 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係得毛姨姨李怡果班幫口兜幫口解釋（當年都有幫青年新政）<br />\n同埋少數連登仔堅持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果呢？大家都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n證明香港人堅守信念落去先係唯一既武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n亦即係當日劉仲敬評論游薏禎果句fucking支那 所謂<span style=\"color: red;\">民族符號</span>"},{"pid":"49e6e7ce09ef5d9051d596a24b4db3d8086c958f","tid":2026208,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T05:18:47.000Z","msg":"香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}